{"tid":936823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"裸照4連發給未成年男生　前選美冠軍+女教師遭起訴","createTime":"2018-12-11T05:29:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-12T07:33:41.000Z","uid":122,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"f7b00f4651cd716bf193c79208161427d706e7dc","tid":936823,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T05:29:09.000Z","msg":"28歲的美國前選美冠軍卡本特(Ramsey Carpenter)涉嫌用手機傳送裸片給一名15歲前男學生，上周四(6日) 在西維吉尼亞州卡諾瓦郡(Kanawha County)被捕。周五她被起訴4項重罪：包括對對未成年人散布或展示猥褻物品。卡本特目前以1萬美元(約30萬元台幣)交保候審。<br />\n<br />\n案情指出，在該郡「安德魯․傑克森中學」(Andrew Jackson Middle School擔任8年級自然課老師的卡本特，在今年8月至10月間，使用通訊體軟體Snapchat至少傳送了4張個人的上空照一名15歲男學生。但近日被學生的父母發現，而且報警。 警方指出，卡本特承認自己的所為，目前已被停職，她任教的學校拒絕對此事發表評論。<br />\n已婚的卡彭特在2014年參選「肯塔基小姐」奪冠，其後代表該州角逐「美利堅小姐」，但未獲名次。她目前已婚，定居在西維珍尼亞州。<br />\n<br />\nready"},{"pid":"0d5c0e3ef066e61e843e06bf5d6bb9451f538d32","tid":936823,"uid":154596,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T05:30:17.000Z","msg":"連登呢？<br />\n連登仔又冇份喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21e8a1b820d3dfc46ef0d04c53f94380c6dec30b","tid":936823,"uid":122,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T05:30:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cfile3.uf.tistory.com/image/992BD64C5AC6E7C11FB147\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile3.uf.tistory.com%2Fimage%2F992BD64C5AC6E7C11FB147&h=7c833c89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nBest Aaron Ramsey"},{"pid":"480edb7092a06f8a50ddbc41c8b91226da7720e7","tid":936823,"uid":39049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T05:31:31.000Z","msg":"快點..."},{"pid":"036b37d55353c81c5ed2572805d3f52c3fd56f0d","tid":936823,"uid":59567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T05:32:20.000Z","msg":"屌j post 永遠係無圖"},{"pid":"67f24cb5c784277a1afc0fd757ec9a498318968d","tid":936823,"uid":24570,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"21e8a1b820d3dfc46ef0d04c53f94380c6dec30b","tid":936823,"uid":122,"lik